-tns-c1812237660-15 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="response-container-header-controls ng-tns-c1812237660-15"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="ng-tns-c1812237660-15 tts ng-trigger ng-trigger-singleResponseEnter ng-star-inserted" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="single-draft-response-container ng-tns-c1812237660-15"><!----></div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="response-container-header-status ng-tns-c1812237660-15"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="response-container-header-processing-state ng-tns-c1812237660-15"></div></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c1812237660-15" jslog="283401;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="2"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1812237660-15 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1812237660-15"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" _nghost-ng-c3909110362="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2533274573="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2533274573="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2533274573="" _nghost-ng-c984046693="" id="message-content-id-r_19038c9756db0500" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c984046693="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color stronger tutor-markdown-rendering" id="model-response-message-contentr_19038c9756db0500" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Website ko URL bata <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="20">.html</code> hatauna (jaslai <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="42">Clean URL</b> wa <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="55">Pretty URL</b> bhaninchha), tapai ko website kahan host bhako chha (Server/Platform) tyo anusar garnu parne hunchha.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Tala sabaibhanda common hosting platforms haru ko lagi tarika diewo chhu:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">1. cPanel / Apache Web Server (Hostinger, Localhost, Shared Hosting)</h3><p data-path-to-node="4">Yadi tapai cPanel wa Apache server use gardai hunuhunchha bhane:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0">Tapai ko website ko main folder (<code data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="33">public_html</code>) ma januhos.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0">Tyaha <code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">.htaccess</code> bhanne file cha ki chhain hernuhos (chhain bhane naya <code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="70">.htaccess</code> file banaunuhos).
<i data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="98">(Note: File hidden huna sakchha, cPanel ma "Show Hidden Files" enable garnuhos).</i></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,0">Tyo <code data-path-to-node="5,2,0" data-index-in-node="4">.htaccess</code> file ma tala ko code paste garnuhos:</p></li></ol><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-30 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block ng-tns-c427156625-30 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_19038c9756db0500&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,&quot;rc_e2a4863566543a5f&quot;,null,null,&quot;gu-Latn&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahcKEwiThO7SwOOVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQOA" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c427156625-30"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c427156625-30"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns-c427156625-30 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-30">Apache</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="buttons ng-tns-c427156625-30 ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" tabindex="-1" type="onSurface" size="small" fonticonname="arrow_circle_down" theme="lm" arialabel="Download code" gemtooltip="Download code" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c427156625-30 gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c374551268="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-32" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c374551268="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-badge mat-unthemed mat-badge-overlap mat-badge-above mat-badge-after mat-badge-small mat-badge-hidden ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-label="Download code" jslog="305704;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c374551268="" _nghost-ng-c818472059=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c818472059="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-l lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="arrow_circle_down" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="arrow_circle_down"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></gem-icon-button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" tabindex="-1" type="onSurface" size="small" fonticonname="copy" theme="lm" arialabel="Copy code" gemtooltip="Copy code" data-test-id="gem-copy-button" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c427156625-30 gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c374551268="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-33" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c374551268="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-badge mat-unthemed mat-badge-overlap mat-badge-above mat-badge-after mat-badge-small mat-badge-hidden ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-label="Copy code" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_19038c9756db0500&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,&quot;rc_e2a4863566543a5f&quot;,null,null,&quot;gu-Latn&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c374551268="" _nghost-ng-c818472059=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c818472059="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-l lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="copy" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="copy"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></gem-icon-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-30"><code _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c427156625-30"><span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteEngine</span></span> <span class="hljs-literal">On</span>

<span class="hljs-comment"># Yadi kohi user le .html lekhera URL kholyo bhane auto .html hataidine (301 Redirect)</span>
<span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteCond</span></span> <span class="hljs-variable">%{THE_REQUEST}</span> ^[A-Z]{<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">9</span>}\ /([^\ ]+)\.html\ HTTP/
<span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteRule</span></span> ^(.*)\.html$ /$<span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-meta"> [R=301,L]</span>

<span class="hljs-comment"># URL ma .html nabhaye pani pachadi bata .html file nai load garne</span>
<span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteCond</span></span> <span class="hljs-variable">%{REQUEST_FILENAME}</span> !-d
<span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteCond</span></span> <span class="hljs-variable">%{REQUEST_FILENAME}</span>\.html -f
<span class="hljs-attribute"><span class="hljs-nomarkup">RewriteRule</span></span> ^(.*)$ $<span class="hljs-number">1</span>.html<span class="hljs-meta"> [L]</span>
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-path-to-node="8">2. Vercel Hosting</h3><p data-path-to-node="9">Yadi tapai ko site <b data-path-to-node="9" data-index-in-node="19">Vercel</b> ma host chha bhane:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="10"><li><p data-path-to-node="10,0,0">Tapai ko project ko main folder (root directory) ma <code data-path-to-node="10,0,0" data-index-in-node="52">vercel.json</code> bhanne file banaunuhos.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="10,1,0">Tyo file ma yo code rakhnuhos:</p></li></ol><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-31 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block ng-tns-c427156625-31 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_19038c9756db0500&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,&quot;rc_e2a4863566543a5f&quot;,null,null,&quot;gu-Latn&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahcKEwiThO7SwOOVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQOQ" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c427156625-31"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c427156625-31"><div