237660-34"></div></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c1812237660-34" jslog="283401;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="2"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1812237660="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1812237660-34 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1812237660-34"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" _nghost-ng-c3909110362="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c815380038="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2533274573="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2533274573="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2533274573="" _nghost-ng-c984046693="" id="message-content-id-r_4811d66b43364257" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c984046693="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color stronger tutor-markdown-rendering" id="model-response-message-contentr_4811d66b43364257" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">GitHub Pages ma site host gardai hunuhunchha bhane <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="51">.html</code> hatauna jhanai sajilo chha. GitHub Pages le by-default kaiyan features automated tarikale support garchha.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Tala dijeka tarika haru madhye jun sajilo lagchha tyo use garnu bhae hunchha:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">Method 1: Direct File Name (Directly Works on GitHub Pages)</h3><p data-path-to-node="4">GitHub Pages ko sabai bhanda ramro kura k chha bhane, tapai ko file ko nam <code data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="75">ai-automation-with-n8n.html</code> chha bhane pani browser ma <code data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="130">.html</code> narakhi open garda (<code data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="156">[https://anillama.com.np/Blogs/ai-automation-with-n8n](https://anillama.com.np/Blogs/ai-automation-with-n8n)</code>) <b data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="266">GitHub Pages le aapei tyo file lai load gari dinchha!</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Garnuparne Kura:</b> Tapai le server ma kehi change garnu pardaina. Bas tapai ko HTML code/navigation menu ma bhako link bata <code data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="122">.html</code> hataideu:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-43 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block ng-tns-c427156625-43 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4811d66b43364257&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,&quot;rc_629c9bb83ccb2ffd&quot;,null,null,&quot;mi&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahcKEwiThO7SwOOVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQVg" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c427156625-43"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c427156625-43"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns