<code data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="36">[https://anillama.com.np/Blogs/ai-automation-with-n8n/](https://anillama.com.np/Blogs/ai-automation-with-n8n/)</code></p><h3 data-path-to-node="12">Method 3: JavaScript Auto Redirect (Manual <code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="43">.html</code> Type Gardani Clean Garna)</h3><p data-path-to-node="13">Yadi kohi user le zabardasti <code data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="29">.html</code> nai lekhera URL open gari halyo bhane, browser address bar bata <code data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="99">.html</code> hatauna tapai le webpage ko <code data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="133">&lt;head&gt;</code> tag bhitra yo sanno JavaScript paste gari dina saknuhunchha:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-44 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block ng-tns-c427156625-44 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4811d66b43364257&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,&quot;rc_629c9bb83ccb2ffd&quot;,null,null,&quot;mi&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahcKEwiThO7SwOOVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQVw" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c427156625-44"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c427156625-44"><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns-c427156625-44 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="ng-tns-c427156625-44">HTML</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" class="buttons ng-tns-c427156625-44 ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c427156625="" tabi