<!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/div&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;div class="toc"&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Table of Contents&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;ol&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;What is n8n?&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Why use AI Automation?&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Installing n8n&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Creating Your First Workflow&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Using Google Sheets&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Connecting AI Models&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Real-world Example&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Best Practices&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Conclusion&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/ol&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/div&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;What is n8n?&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;n8n is an open-source workflow automation platform that allows you to connect different applications without writing large amounts of code. You can automate repetitive work, move data between apps, trigger notifications, call APIs, and integrate AI models into business processes.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Why AI Automation?&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;Businesses spend countless hours performing repetitive tasks such as copying data, replying to emails, updating spreadsheets, and generating reports. AI automation combines intelligent models with workflow automation to reduce manual effort, improve accuracy, and save time.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Installing n8n&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;The easiest way is with Docker. After installation, access the editor in your browser and start building workflows visually using drag-and-drop nodes.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Creating Your First Workflow&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;A simple workflow could:&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Receive a form submission&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Store the data in Google Sheets&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Ask an AI model to summarize the request&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Send a confirmation email&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Google Sheets Integration&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;Google Sheets is commonly used as a lightweight database. n8n can read, update, append, and search rows automatically, making it perfect for small business automation.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Connecting AI Models&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;You can connect OpenAI-compatible APIs or other LLM providers to classify text, generate content, summarize documents, translate languages, or answer customer queries.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Real-World Example&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;One practical workflow is an e-commerce order automation system:&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Read new orders from Google Sheets.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Validate customer information.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Calculate delivery charges using an API.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Create a delivery request automatically.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Update the order status.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Notify the customer.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Best Practices&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Use descriptive node names.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Handle errors gracefully.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Keep credentials secure.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Test workflows before production.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;li&gt;Monitor execution history regularly.&lt;/li&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/ul&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;n8n is one of the most powerful automation tools available today. Whether you are a freelancer, developer, entrepreneur, or business owner, learning n8n can dramatically improve productivity. Combining AI with workflow automation opens the door to smarter, faster, and more scalable business processes.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;h2&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Is n8n free?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yes, the self-hosted version is open source.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can beginners learn n8n?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Absolutely. The visual interface makes it beginner friendly.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can I use AI with n8n?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Yes. You can integrate AI APIs for content generation, summarization, classification, and more.&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;hr&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;p&gt;© 2026 Anil Lama • anillama.com.np&lt;/p&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/body&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> &lt;/html&gt; <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> yae same format ma malai euta blog banayera deu na <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> How AI is growing in the world. <!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" aria-hidden="true" class="luminous-collapse-spacer ng-star-inserted"></span><!----></p><!----></div><!----></span><div _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="luminous-toggle-container ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" mat-icon-button="" theme="lm" aria-label="Collapse" gemtooltip="Collapse text" data-test-id="luminous-collapse-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger luminous-toggle-button mat-unthemed lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="224551;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_529c8aa8438d187d&quot;,&quot;c_85d3c3c486cd93a7&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]];mutable:true" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-46" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><div _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" data-test-id="luminous-collapse-pill" class="luminous-toggle-pill"><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" fonticonname="expand_less" size="medium" _nghost-ng-c818472059=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c818472059="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-m lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_less" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="expand_less"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon></div><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></span><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" class="luminous-actions-container ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c2124663650="" tabindex="-1" theme="lm" type="translucent" arialabel="Copy prompt" gemtool